content:
Pity that I didn't take a Before photo. My front door was so weathered that the wood was nearly white 
 However, Mr Duncan Farrugia came to the rescue and now my door is as good as new. He doesn't know that I am writing this but I think it is the least I can do to thank him for his outstanding work. His FB page is Restorations on Wood 77300900. Highly recommend from my end (and I consider myself as a very hard to please person when it comes to such works 
)
